# Never commit third-party / game binaries.
# The ONLY DLL that belongs in this repo is our own compiled shim,
# amd_ags_x64.dll (built from src/). Everything below is either the user's
# own game files (copied locally at install time) or build junk.

# The original AMD DLL is copied from the user's game install by install.sh.
# It must never end up in the repo.
amd_ags_orig.dll
*_orig.dll

# Any other stray game/engine binaries or archives
*.rda
d3d12*.dll
dxgi*.dll
sl.*.dll
nvngx*.dll
nvapi*.dll

# Build / OS junk
*.o
*.obj
*.exe
.DS_Store
